(ooc: preds couldn't destroy the element, jp, they're two whimpy :)

Element watched Divebomb fly away from him and turned his attention back to 
the CF, looking at all the bots that were firing. His eyes surveyed the 
sight, and then fell upon Hell Beast. Element ran forward and launched 
several missiles at Hell Beast, mentally guiding them toward him.


Cyndro saw that the bots he had been firing at were running, but he fired 
after them with EMP blasts, seeking missiles, and normal laser fire. They 
wern't going to get away that easy! :)
